   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Pemsas to Philon, greeting. You must know that the animals of Horos have been taken in pledge by the guard of Ptolemaios. You will therefore do well, if you think fit, to certify Ptolemaios that some one will make an arrangement. Goodbye. (Addressed on the verso) To Philon.</ab>
